tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE price_data (
    exchange_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    token_id INT,
    price DECIMAL(18,6),
    volume DECIMAL(18,6),
    timestamp TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE decentralized_exchanges (
   id INT PRIMARY KEY,
   exchange_name VARCHAR(50),
   token_pair VARCHAR(50),
   price DECIMAL(12, 4),
   time TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE analyzed_prices (
   id INT PRIMARY KEY,
   token_pair VARCHAR(50),
   average_price DECIMAL(12, 4),
   highest_price DECIMAL(12, 4),
   lowest_price DECIMAL(12, 4),
   analysis_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE exchange_prices (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    exchange_id INT,
    token_id INT,
    price DECIMAL,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    FOREIGN KEY (exchange_id) REFERENCES decentralized_exchanges(id),
    FOREIGN KEY (token_id) REFERENCES tokens(id)
);

CREATE TABLE price_data (
	price_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	exchange_id INT NOT NULL,
	token_id INT NOT NULL,
	price DECIMAL(18,8) NOT NULL,
	timestamp TIMESTAMP NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE analysis_data (
	analysis_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	token_id INT NOT NULL,
	average_price DECIMAL(18,8) NOT NULL,
	high_price DECIMAL(18,8) NOT NULL,
	low_price DECIMAL(18,8) NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE prices (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    token_id INT NOT NULL,
    exchange_id INT NOT NULL,
    price DECIMAL(18, 8) NOT NULL,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE transactions (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    token_id INT NOT NULL,
    exchange_id INT NOT NULL,
    volume DECIMAL(18, 8) NOT NULL,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP NOT NULL
);
